1
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:44,150
<涅盘经>第十九卷
< Nirvana Sutra > Verse 19

2
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:46,640
八大地狱之最 称为无间地狱
The worst of the Eight Hells is called Continuous Hell

3
00:02:46,830 --> 00:02:50,820
为无间断遭受大苦之意 故有此名
It has the meaning of Continuous Suffering. Thus the name

4
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,250
五年前
5 years ago

5
00:03:25,410 --> 00:03:26,670
屯门大兴村
we started valet parking in Tuen Mun.

6
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:30,210
皇宫大酒楼门口的停车档
at Palace Restaurant in Tai Hing Estate

7
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,340
开张大吉
Tuen Mun.

8
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:37,390
我和弟兄们雄心壮志
We were full of ambition.

9
00:03:38,330 --> 00:03:40,320
谁知道开张还不到半个月
But 2 weeks had hardly gone by

10
00:03:41,410 --> 00:03:44,710
每天平均被人扫荡一点三次
and the cops started busting us every day.

11
00:03:47,790 --> 00:03:49,080
一年内
Within one year

12
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,790
死了六个兄弟
6 of our brothers died.

13
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:03,800
佛祖保佑
Thanks to the Buddha, my life has been spared.

14
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:15,790
算命的说我是 "一将功成万骨枯"
"What thousands must die so that Caesar may become great."

15
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,460
不过我不同意
But I don't believe in destiny.

16
00:04:20,410 --> 00:04:22,380
我认为出来混的
The rule of this game

17
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:26,080
是生是死要由自己决定
is to take fate in our own hands.

18
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:29,380
你们跟着我的日子最短
You are the newest in my gang.

19
00:04:31,620 --> 00:04:33,210
底子最干净
Your records are the cleanest.

20
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:39,020
路怎么走 让你们自己挑啊
You can choose your own future.

21
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:46,780
好了
OK.

22
00:04:49,080 --> 00:04:50,570
祝你们
I wish you guys

23
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,830
在警察部一帆风顺
every success in the police force.

24
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:58,230
干杯 各位长官
Bottoms up, officers.

25
00:05:16,580 --> 00:05:17,340
27149
27149

26
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,680
十分钟前你进来过
you were here 10 minutes ago.

27
00:05:19,660 --> 00:05:20,920
我桌上有几个档案夹?
How many files were on my desk?

28
00:05:22,330 --> 00:05:24,420
六个 四个米色在左边
Six, sir. Four beige ones on the left

29
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:26,690
一个红色和一个白色在右边 长官
one red and one white on the right.

30
00:05:32,540 --> 00:05:34,060
你觉得我这人人怎么样?
What do you think of me?

31
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,600
对不起长官 不清楚
Sorry, I'm not sure, sir.

32
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,490
不过长官今天早上应该很匆忙
But I know you're in a hurry today

33
00:05:40,660 --> 00:05:42,060
因为您穿了不同的袜子
'coz your socks don't match.

34
00:05:49,370 --> 00:05:51,030
27149 先出去
27149, you can go now.

35
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:52,260
是 长官
Yes, sir.

36
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,000
五百 快点给钱
You owe me $500.

37
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,320
行了 下个月发了薪水再给你
Okay, but wait till pay day next month.

38
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,800
我说了,他最适合做卧底
I told you he would make the best undercover cop

39
00:06:06,290 --> 00:06:08,950
进了警校,就要遵守警校的规矩
Now that you're in the cadet school you should follow the rules

40
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,360
不守规矩的人,就好像他这样
Those who break the rules will be like him

41
00:06:11,580 --> 00:06:12,640
滚蛋
They will be expelled

42
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:19,080
有没有人想跟他交换?
Who wants to trade place with him?

43
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,130
我想跟他换
I do

44
00:06:37,580 --> 00:06:38,440
27149
27149

45
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:40,860
这是个长时间的卧底计划
this is a long-term undercover mission

46
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,100
你在警察学校的记录会被删除
Your records in the cadet school will be erased

47
00:06:43,410 --> 00:06:44,740
只有我和重案组的黄督察
Only Superintendent Wong and I

48
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,050
知道你的身份
know of your identity

49
00:06:46,370 --> 00:06:48,430
你接受的是一个非常危险的任务
This mission is highly dangerous

50
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:49,950
你清楚了吗?
is that clear?

51
00:06:50,330 --> 00:06:51,190
是,长官
Yes, sir

52
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:55,020
黄Sir,我真的撑不下去啦
Sir, I can't stand it any longer

53
00:06:55,500 --> 00:06:57,050
不是被警察骚扰
I'm either harassed by cops

54
00:06:57,330 --> 00:06:58,760
就是被古惑仔打
or beaten up by gangsters

55
00:06:59,910 --> 00:07:02,280
4927,你是新人
4927, you are still a rookie

56
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:05,030
凭什么令我满意推荐你升级?
Give me a good reason why I should promote you

57
00:07:05,910 --> 00:07:09,400
撑,你来试试啊,怎么撑啊
Hang on? Why don't you go hang yourself instead?

58
00:07:10,950 --> 00:07:12,680
我在警校拿了优异奖
I won the Silver Whistle Award at the cadet

59
00:07:12,910 --> 00:07:14,540
在学期间获得了高度评价
and have received numerous kudos as an officer

60
00:07:14,790 --> 00:07:17,050
长官,我有信心可以领导警队
I am confident I can lead the police force sir

61
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,930
琛哥
Boss

62
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,550
是，知道了
OK, I got it

63
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:36,120
走
Move forward

64
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:37,480
快点
Hurry up

65
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:43,950
现在你到那边去拍张照
Please go over there to take your mugshot

66
00:08:22,290 --> 00:08:23,050
请问
Excuse me

67
00:08:24,370 --> 00:08:25,300
- 有没有人? - 什么事
- Hello? - Can I help you?

68
00:08:26,660 --> 00:08:28,860
啊 没有没有 我想试试那个
Can I try this stereo?

69
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:30,750
你用什么喇叭?
What speakers are you using?

70
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:33,340
没有 有什么好介绍的?
Nothing special, any recommendations?

71
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:38,860
这部 标准港产货 一万多
Try this tube amplifier, made in Hong Kong, 10 grand only.

72
00:08:41,790 --> 00:08:43,380
加上千多块的本地线
And use this cable, also locally made about 1000.

73
00:08:43,660 --> 00:08:44,960
比得上十几万的欧洲货
The sound is as good as expensive European amps.

74
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:49,180
高音甜 中音准 低音沉
Sweet high notes, crisp middle, strong bass.

75
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,460
总之一句话 就是通透
In a word, transparent.

76
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,560
来 过来听听
Come and listen.

77
00:09:02,330 --> 00:09:03,990
立体感多强
Human voices are drifting towards you.

78
00:09:06,290 --> 00:09:07,650
感觉到没有?
See that?

79
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:11,730
就好像在你面前唱一样
Voices are indeed drifting towards you.

80
00:09:23,950 --> 00:09:26,220
你试试这个
Try this one.

81
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,860
你听老音乐呢 这种好
This is ideal for listening to oldies.

82
00:09:35,830 --> 00:09:36,950
怎么样?
What do you think?

83
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,510
真的不错
Much better indeed.

84
00:09:41,330 --> 00:09:44,020
要是我买一整套 有折扣没有?
Any discount if I buy the whole set?

85
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:45,970
胆机在这儿买
Buy the tube amp here

86
00:09:46,660 --> 00:09:47,820
喇叭就不要了
but not the speakers.

87
00:09:48,830 --> 00:09:50,090
祥威便宜点
Go to Cheung Wai; it's cheaper there.

88
00:09:52,290 --> 00:09:53,350
我找谁啊?
Whom should I ask for?

89
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,700
你就说阿仁介绍的
Just tell them Yan sent you.

90
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:03,300
哪张是我的?
Which one is mine?

91
00:10:03,500 --> 00:10:04,260
中间那张
The one in the middle.

92
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:05,960
OK 谢谢
Okay, thanks.

93
00:10:06,290 --> 00:10:07,220
谢了
You're welcome.

94
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:09,650
现在去祥威有人在吗?
Is Cheung Wai open yet?

95
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:10,820
有啦
Sure.

96
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:12,680
喂 你臭小子
You bastard.

97
00:10:12,950 --> 00:10:15,050
我叫你帮我看着 你吃里爬外
I told you to watch the store not to send my customers away.

98
00:10:15,290 --> 00:10:17,190
你的喇叭是卖得贵嘛
But your speakers are over-priced.

99
00:10:17,410 --> 00:10:18,500
我不卖贵点
If I don't sell them at this price

100
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:21,310
哪有钱交保护费给你们这些老大呀?
how can I afford to pay "protection money"?

101
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:23,280
那你不交试试看啦
You can try not paying for a change.

102
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:25,230
哎 我的线
Hey, the cable.

103
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:26,220
借用两天
I'll return it in a few days.

104
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:28,590
四千多块 你借用两天
$4,000 for a few days?

105
00:10:28,830 --> 00:10:29,560
去哪儿呀?
Where are you rushing to?

106
00:10:29,870 --> 00:10:30,770
去送殡
A funeral.

107
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:01,210
你说
Tell me.

108
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:03,680
你光是伤人已经好几次了
How many times have you been busted for assault?

109
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,830
我千方百计和律政司说
I am trying to convince the Department of Justice

110
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,950
你心理有问题
that you have psychological problems

111
00:11:07,150 --> 00:11:08,380
叫你看心理医生
and need to see a shrink.

112
00:11:08,580 --> 00:11:09,770
你还到处打人
But you keep on beating people up.

113
00:11:12,870 --> 00:11:14,630
你是不是真的心理变态?
Are you really going nuts?

114
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,850
你忘了自己是好人还是坏人了?
Have you forgotten you're a cop?

115
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:23,540
明明说好三年 三年之后又三年
You told me it's only for 3 years.

116
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:25,490
三年之后又三年
But after 3 years come another 3 years, and another.

117
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:30,020
就快十年了 老大
It's almost 10 years already, boss.

118
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:33,580
你对我态度好点行不行?
Can't you be a bit more courteous to me?

119
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:36,430
现在全香港只有我知道你的身份
I'm the only one in Hong Kong who knows your real identity now.

120
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,300
我回去把你的档案全都删除掉
Maybe I'll just erase your file

121
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:40,270
你一辈子做古惑仔 我也不用烦了
so you can stick with the Triads for good.

122
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,000
你想我怎么样
What do you want me to do?

123
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:46,530
天天提醒自己 我是警察
Remind myself I'm a cop every day?

124
00:11:47,290 --> 00:11:48,750
做梦的时候都说
Shouting out "Drop your gun, I'm a cop."

125
00:11:49,410 --> 00:11:52,110
"放下枪 我是警察!"这样?
even in my dreams?

126
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,100
韩琛什么时候进货?
When will Sam place his order?

127
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,300
不知道
No idea.

128
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:09,080
这个星期
Sometime this week.

129
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:09,990
什么?
What?

130
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,360
这个星期之内
Sometime this week.

131
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:15,510
泰国佬已经来了
The Thais are here.

132
00:12:15,830 --> 00:12:17,690
韩琛收了货 去卖给别人
Once the goods arrive, Sam will resell them.

133
00:12:20,750 --> 00:12:21,680
货仓在哪儿?
Where is the warehouse?

134
00:12:21,910 --> 00:12:23,810
我怎么知道那货仓在哪儿?
How the hell do I know?

135
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,670
我才跟了他三年
I started working for him only 3 years ago.

136
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:31,090
这案子一破就退休
Okay, I'll let you retire after this.

137
00:12:31,330 --> 00:12:32,490
你少来
Bullshit.

138
00:12:32,790 --> 00:12:34,550
这句话我听了九千多次
I heard this a zillion times already.

139
00:12:49,410 --> 00:12:51,280
又是这些破玩意儿(偷听器)?
Shit. These mikes again?

140
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:52,620
警察部那么有钱
The Police is loaded with cash

141
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:54,540
能不能换点先进的
tell them to get more advanced models.

142
00:12:55,410 --> 00:12:57,140
植入体内的 要不要?
How about implanting it into your body?

143
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,320
植在哪儿?
Into which part of my body?

144
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:11,380
针孔摄影机
A pinhole camera?

145
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,190
针孔在哪?
Where's the lens?

146
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:18,480
二十五号是你生日嘛 臭小子
Your birthday is on the 25th, right?

147
00:13:21,120 --> 00:13:23,020
我从来不戴表
I never wear watches.

148
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,170
怎么样?
So?

149
00:13:57,580 --> 00:14:00,740
如果五点前不把数据交给国际刑警
If we got nothing for the Interpol by 5pm

150
00:14:01,370 --> 00:14:03,070
假护照这个案子就麻烦了
the counterfeit passport case is off.

151
00:14:03,290 --> 00:14:04,550
三点一刻啦
3:15. Tea time.

152
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,140
头儿 喝什么?
What would you like, boss?

153
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:08,720
热奶茶
Tea with milk, please.

154
00:14:09,290 --> 00:14:12,190
他们什么都不肯说全部都说要等律师来
They won't talk without their attorney.

155
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:14,420
那些律师到现在还没回复
Has paged their lawyers but he hasn't called back yet.

156
00:14:46,750 --> 00:14:49,180
律师没来 我什么都不会说
I won't talk without my attorney.

157
00:14:52,040 --> 00:14:53,270
我是刘律师
I am Mr. Lau, your attorney.

158
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:55,460
有没有打电话回家?
Did you call home?

159
00:14:59,410 --> 00:15:00,900
打回去干吗?
Why should I call home?

160
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:03,860
没打就好
It's good then.

161
00:15:04,200 --> 00:15:05,300
上个星期五 十七号
Where were you

162
00:15:05,580 --> 00:15:06,940
下午三点四十五分到五点
last friday

163
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:08,290
你去哪里了?
from 3:45 to 5:00 pm?

164
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:10,460
毛哥叫我来问你
Brother Mo told me to ask you

165
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:12,300
家里有没有什么要帮忙的
if yourfamily needs any help.

166
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:16,440
不用到处看
No need to look around.

167
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:18,220
律师在这儿 警察不可以录像
They won't record anything when a lawyer is present.

168
00:15:18,450 --> 00:15:19,510
录下来也没用
It's not admissible in court anyway.

169
00:15:31,370 --> 00:15:32,700
毛哥叫你来的?
Brother Mo sent you?

170
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,820
隔壁你那两个手下
Those 2 kids next door

171
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:40,140
把货场工厂供出来了
have squealed on the workshop already.

172
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,790
现在警察正赶过去
Cops are heading there now.

173
00:15:42,830 --> 00:15:46,390
毛哥叫我来通知你 别乱说话
Brother Mo told you not to say anything.

174
00:15:48,790 --> 00:15:50,780
如果有亲弟弟在那儿
If your brother is there

175
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:52,700
通知他
tell him to leave right away.

176
00:15:53,870 --> 00:15:54,860
叫他先走
Here.

177
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:11,300
怎么样?
What?

178
00:16:11,700 --> 00:16:12,900
走啊
Scram.

179
00:16:13,370 --> 00:16:15,300
叫你走啊 听见没有?
I ask you to scram, do you hear?

180
00:16:15,580 --> 00:16:17,100
快点走啊
Scram right away.

181
00:16:20,330 --> 00:16:22,820
好 那我先走
All right! I'll leave you.

182
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:27,180
既然你不信
If you don't trust me, so be it.

183
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,360
自己小心点
Take care.

184
00:16:33,250 --> 00:16:36,840
对了 律师没来之前 千万别乱说话
Remember don't talk without your attorney

185
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,420
还用你教我
I don't need you to tell me that.

186
00:16:41,500 --> 00:16:42,090
Fanny.
Fanny.

187
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:42,950
哎
Yes?

188
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:43,780
来
Take this.

189
00:16:45,330 --> 00:16:46,090
打电话
Check this number.

190
00:16:46,290 --> 00:16:47,080
行啦
Sure.

191
00:16:47,330 --> 00:16:48,450
帮我把消息发出去
Send this message for me.

192
00:16:56,950 --> 00:16:58,920
牛头角长辉工业大厦二楼
Ngau Tau Kok Cheung Fai Industrial Building, 2nd Floor.

193
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,940
查到了
Get it.

194
00:17:00,250 --> 00:17:04,160
牛头角长辉工业大厦二楼 OK
Ngau Tau Kok, Cheung Fai Industrial Building, 2nd Floor. OK.

