00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:10,960
一个人把一张牌摆在对方的口袋里
They each put a playing card into the other's pocket.

395
00:34:11,160 --> 00:34:14,830
谁猜到对方拿什么牌放到自己的口袋里谁就算赢
Whoever guesses the card in their own pocket wins.

396
00:34:17,080 --> 00:34:18,600
你知道我看你什么牌了
You know I can see your card.

397
00:34:20,830 --> 00:34:22,460
我都相信是
I think so too.

398
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,520
我赢定了
I will beat you.

399
00:34:28,870 --> 00:34:29,770
行了
Let's see.

400
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:33,210
好 大家小心点
We should be more careful.

401
00:34:33,410 --> 00:34:34,280
好
I will.

402
00:34:35,120 --> 00:34:36,610
哦 忘了告诉你了
By the way

403
00:34:37,290 --> 00:34:38,950
如果谁输的话就会死
whoever loses the game will die.

404
00:34:41,660 --> 00:34:43,560
看你什么时候死
Let's see when you're gonna die.

405
00:34:48,500 --> 00:34:50,860
你见过有人去摈仪馆和死尸握手吗
Ever seen someone shakes a corpse's hand?

406
00:34:55,250 --> 00:34:56,040
走
Let's go.

407
00:35:17,370 --> 00:35:18,270
放沙发旁边好了
Put it next to the couch.

408
00:35:18,410 --> 00:35:19,210
好
OK.

409
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,390
谢谢
Thanks.

410
00:35:24,000 --> 00:35:25,360
Mary
Mary

411
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:27,400
装修师傅几号电话?
What's interior designer's number?

412
00:35:27,660 --> 00:35:31,620
装修师傅 90255047
The interior designer... 90255047.

413
00:35:33,750 --> 00:35:35,140
哎哟 我刚才数到第几箱啦?
How many boxes have I counted?

414
00:35:36,290 --> 00:35:37,690
24
24

415
00:35:37,950 --> 00:35:39,550
24?真的?
24? Are you sure?

416
00:35:39,700 --> 00:35:40,860
Sure(真的)
Sure

417
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:44,460
把电话给我
Pass me the phone.

418
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,760
哦 来来来
Coming.

419
00:35:50,410 --> 00:35:51,610
喂?
Hello?

420
00:35:52,330 --> 00:35:52,730
哦 等等啊
Hold on please.

421
00:35:52,910 --> 00:35:53,710
干什么?谁啊?
Who is it?

422
00:35:53,870 --> 00:35:54,630
不知道
I don't know.

423
00:35:54,910 --> 00:35:55,940
喂
Hello.

424
00:35:56,250 --> 00:35:57,110
是我
It's me.

425
00:35:57,330 --> 00:35:59,090
对 在搬家呢
Yes, I'm moving in.

426
00:35:59,330 --> 00:36:01,320
别偷听 在说秘密
Don't eavesdrop. It's confidential.

427
00:36:02,200 --> 00:36:03,260
我整批货没了
I lost all of my goods.

428
00:36:04,250 --> 00:36:05,010
查一下
There's a mole.

429
00:36:05,330 --> 00:36:06,260
谁是卧底
Dig him outfor me.

430
00:36:06,450 --> 00:36:07,890
你等等 这人多
Hold on, too many people around here.

431
00:36:08,040 --> 00:36:09,000
等等
Hold on.

432
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:13,110
卧底的档案我不能碰 我查不到
I have no access to those undercoverfiles. I can't dig him out.

433
00:36:13,450 --> 00:36:14,750
我不管有多困难
I don't care how difficult it is.

434
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:19,220
我只知道他用的是摩斯密码
I only know he uses Morse codes.

435
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:30,070
那好 你把昨天晚上那些人的资料全都给我
Give me all the information on the people around you last night.

436
00:36:30,330 --> 00:36:33,960
真名啦 身份证啦 银行号码
Their real names, ID card no., account no., etc.

437
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:36,860
今晚见 13楼
See you tonight, at the cinema

438
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:37,960
就这样
OK.

439
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:44,560
怎么了?
What's the matter?

440
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:49,630
29
29

441
00:36:50,950 --> 00:36:52,150
28
28

442
00:36:52,500 --> 00:36:53,830
29啊
29

443
00:36:54,040 --> 00:36:55,970
我在说我的小说 我写的那本小说
I'm talking about my novel.

444
00:36:56,250 --> 00:36:57,800
我想到写什么了 来来来 过来 过来
I know what I'm going to write about. Come here.

445
00:36:59,080 --> 00:37:02,100
我可以写那个男主角有二十八种性格
I can write about a man with 28 different personalities.

446
00:37:02,660 --> 00:37:03,490
你是说我啊?
Are you talking about me?

447
00:37:03,750 --> 00:37:05,080
你正经一点嘛
Be more serious.

448
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:06,500
喂 你想一想啊
Think about it.

449
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:08,610
一个人有二十八种性格
A man with 28 personalities.

450
00:37:08,830 --> 00:37:11,660
也就是说 他每天起床就自己跟自己演戏
That means he starts role playing the minute he wakes up.

451
00:37:11,910 --> 00:37:13,070
演得他连自己的
He is no longer certain

452
00:37:13,330 --> 00:37:14,390
真实性格都忘了
which personality is the real him.

453
00:37:15,790 --> 00:37:16,780
是不是很恐怖啊?
Isn't it scary?

454
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:17,830
很恐怖嘛
Very much.

455
00:37:18,450 --> 00:37:19,250
很棒的
Good?

456
00:37:19,500 --> 00:37:20,550
很棒 一定很畅销
Yeah. Will be a bestsellerfor sure.

457
00:37:20,790 --> 00:37:21,380
喂 等等等等
Wait...

458
00:37:21,580 --> 00:37:22,140
干嘛?
What is it?

459
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:23,550
凳子为什么这么大啊?
Why is the ottoman so big?

460
00:37:24,080 --> 00:37:25,010
哪张啊?
Which one?

461
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:28,630
哎呀 我尺寸量大了 量错了
I must have gotten the measurements wrong.

462
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:31,470
你别这样 你别这样哦
Take it easy.

463
00:37:31,790 --> 00:37:33,150
你们这些女孩子啊...
You women...

464
00:37:33,410 --> 00:37:35,240
行了 行了 让我来看啊
Let me see. Get up slowly.

465
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,210
你别发脾气
Don't be mad.

466
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:44,190
见面?
Meet up?

467
00:37:44,450 --> 00:37:45,350
你想我死呀?
You want me dead?

468
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:47,050
现在警局里有鬼
There's a mole in the police station

469
00:37:47,410 --> 00:37:48,640
你先把他揪出来
Dig him outfirst.

470
00:37:50,330 --> 00:37:51,490
那谁是啊?
So who is he?

471
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:54,290
好 我不跟你说了
I can't talk anymore.

472
00:37:55,660 --> 00:37:56,590
什么?
What?

473
00:37:57,410 --> 00:37:58,470
刚才?
Just now?

474
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:00,180
看跌打医生啊
I was at a Chinese chiropractor.

475
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:03,190
现在看心理医生
I'm seeing the shrink now.

476
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,900
我心理变态呀!就这样
I'm going psycho. That's it.

477
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:07,590
哇 这张椅子真是...太棒了
This chair is really... incredible.

478
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:10,300
那你应该买一张回家
Why don't you get one for yourself?

479
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:12,050
不用每次都来这边睡
So you don't need to come here and sleep every time.

480
00:39:12,370 --> 00:39:13,670
你这里舒服一点嘛
It's more comfortable here.

481
00:39:15,160 --> 00:39:16,460
别这么小器
Don't be so peevish.

482
00:39:16,830 --> 00:39:19,320
这四个月 要不是我每个星期来睡一觉
During these 4 months, if it weren't for me

483
00:39:19,830 --> 00:39:21,300
你那有时间打游戏机
you wouldn't have the time to play computer games.

484
00:39:23,330 --> 00:39:24,800
是五个月
It's 5 months.

485
00:39:26,580 --> 00:39:28,640
还有一个月 你的强制性治疗就结束
In one more month, your mandatory therapy will be over.

486
00:39:28,870 --> 00:39:30,530
到时你能回家慢慢睡了
You can sleep peacefully at home then.

487
00:39:31,950 --> 00:39:33,220
这么快结束啊?
So soon?

488
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:36,740
但是我好像没什么进展
I don't seem to have improved at all.

489
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:39,930
要不你写个报告 让我多看一段时间
Why don't you just prolong my treatment.

490
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:44,250
哦对 还有 最近我的头呢...好像要裂开似的
Besides, my head is splitting these days.

491
00:39:44,790 --> 00:39:46,480
会不会是精神分裂啊??
Could it be schizophrenia?

492
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:49,860
这叫头痛 我开点必理痛给你
This is called "headache". I'll prescribe some Panadol for you.

493
00:39:53,830 --> 00:39:55,260
其实有件事我想问你
Actually, there's something I want to ask you

494
00:39:55,500 --> 00:39:56,460
但又觉得
but...

495
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:58,600
好像有点不太好意思
it's kind of embarrassing.

496
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,390
你觉得我人怎么样?
What do you think of me?

497
00:40:06,910 --> 00:40:09,680
就是说 你觉得我是一个好人呢 还是个坏人?
Do you think I'm a good guy or a bad guy?

498
00:40:11,120 --> 00:40:12,550
我都不知道你是什么人
I hardly know who you are.

499
00:40:20,500 --> 00:40:23,520
告诉你一个秘密 不要告诉别人
Tell you a secret, but don't tell anyone.

500
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,200
其实我是警察
I'm actually a cop.

501
00:40:34,870 --> 00:40:36,100
我也是
So am I.

502
00:40:44,290 --> 00:40:45,550
下个星期继续
Let's continue nextweek.

503
00:40:45,910 --> 00:40:47,380
要记住你做过的梦
Try to remember your dreams.

504
00:40:48,410 --> 00:40:49,400
记得
Of course.

505
00:40:50,500 --> 00:40:51,430
梦见你咯
I will dream about you.

506
00:40:53,370 --> 00:40:54,360
下星期见
See you nextweek.

507
00:40:58,500 --> 00:40:59,660
真的只有必理痛?
Just Panadol?

508
00:41:05,750 --> 00:41:06,610
再见
Bye.

509
00:41:12,410 --> 00:41:14,310
你的升职报告没问题
Your promotion should be OK.

510
00:41:15,870 --> 00:41:17,460
我会调你到内务部
You will be transferred to Internal Affairs

511
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:19,640
不过在重案组上班
but you will work at OCTB.

512
00:41:21,660 --> 00:41:22,560
不明白
I don't understand.

513
00:41:24,330 --> 00:41:27,390
韩琛的案子没破 我怀疑有内鬼
I suspect Sam has a mole in the department.

514
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:28,680
想你去查一下
I want you to investigate.

515
00:41:29,330 --> 00:41:30,320
为什么要我去?
Why me?

516
00:41:31,200 --> 00:41:34,200
我和老张 老陈选了很久了
We have scrutinized all possible candidates.

517
00:41:34,620 --> 00:41:36,090
你是最合适的人选
You have an immaculate record

518
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:38,630
在情报科破了不少案子
and you have solved many cases in CIB.

519
00:41:39,410 --> 00:41:43,110
做内部调查有机会接触管理层啊
Working in IA, you will get in touch with senior officials.

520
00:41:43,500 --> 00:41:44,930
这是机会
That's a good opportunity.

521
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:48,960
对了 下星期我安排你上《警讯》
I've arranged for you to appear on TV.

522
00:41:49,500 --> 00:41:50,690
打扮得帅一点
Remember to spruce up a bit. bit.

523
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,380
那我什么时候面试?
When will I meet the Board?

524
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:57,190
刚才已经面试啦
You just did.

525
00:41:58,000 --> 00:42:01,660
来 你来试试 来 玩玩嘛
Come, take a stab.

526
00:42:06,160 --> 00:42:07,060
谢谢
Thanks.

527
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:08,980
对了
By the way

528
00:42:09,830 --> 00:42:11,890
你的婚礼筹备的怎么样?
how's the wedding?

529
00:42:12,410 --> 00:42:13,470
差不多了
Everything's on schedule.

530
00:42:14,450 --> 00:42:15,480
这就好
That's good.

531
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:18,830
快点结婚 人也会定性一点
You'll be more stable after marriage.

532
00:42:19,160 --> 00:42:20,560
给大家一个好印象嘛
Your image will improve too.

533
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:22,690
你还有机会升的
You have chance offurther promotion.

534
00:42:25,580 --> 00:42:27,840
对了 什么都要看长远一点
Yes, broaden your horizon.

535
00:42:31,330 --> 00:42:32,800
要写真名字的
Fill in your real name.

536
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,200
这是我的真名啊
This is my real name.

537
00:42:34,830 --> 00:42:36,320
你不知我叫迪比亚路啊?
You don't know Del Piero is my real name?

538
00:42:36,500 --> 00:42:37,260
真的啊?
Is that so?

539
00:42:37,450 --> 00:42:38,350
真的
Yes.

540
00:42:46,330 --> 00:42:47,630
喂 填什么哪?
What are you guys writing?

541
00:42:48,080 --> 00:42:52,070
哦 琛哥说 要交点资料上去
The Boss told us to fill in these forms.

542
00:42:52,410 --> 00:42:54,900
一定是帮我们买强积金的
Must be setting up mandatory providentfunds for us.

543
00:42:55,160 --> 00:42:56,220
MPF
You know, MPF.

544
00:42:59,330 --> 00:43:00,160
哇 你这么大个人
Are you serious?

545
00:43:00,410 --> 00:43:01,850
保镖的镖都写错?
You don't even know to spell "bodyguard"?

546
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:02,600
不是这个啊?
Isn't it supposed to look like this?

547
00:43:02,830 --> 00:43:04,020
当然不是这个啦
Of course not.

548
00:43:18,040 --> 00:43:19,470
木字边的嘛
Should be B-O-D-Y-G-A-R-D.

549
00:43:19,750 --> 00:43:20,940
是这个呀
That's it.

550
00:43:46,870 --> 00:43:47,930
下个礼拜进货
A shipmentwill come in nextweek.

551
00:43:49,540 --> 00:43:50,600
风声紧
They are watching closely.

552
00:43:51,660 --> 00:43:52,920
你做你的事
You do what you need to do.

553
00:43:54,200 --> 00:43:55,500
我这边你不用担心管
I'll handle the rest.

554
00:43:57,330 --> 00:43:59,730
正在查内鬼 我怕我帮不了你
The file is open. I'm afraid I can't handle it.

555
00:44:00,200 --> 00:44:01,970
原来你不是担心我
So you're notworried about me.

556
00:44:03,450 --> 00:44:05,650
你是担心你自己啊 刘警官
You are worried about yourself, Inspector Lau.

557
00:44:09,750 --> 00:44:11,540
哇 这女的长这么丑啊
Those girls are so ugly.

558
00:44:22,200 --> 00:44:23,690
尽快帮你办妥
I'll take care of it as soon as I can.

559
00:45:26,620 --> 00:45:27,610
喂?
Hello?

560
00:45:31,330 --> 00:45:32,690
现在回来
I'm on my way back.

561
00:46:16,660 --> 00:46:17,960
阿仁
Yan.

562
00:46:19,660 --> 00:46:20,890
跟我多久了?
How long have you worked for me?

563
00:46:21,700 --> 00:46:23,070
三 四年了吧
3 or 4 years already.

564
00:46:23,660 --> 00:46:24,750
有这么久吗?
That long?

565
00:46:25,450 --> 00:46:26,750
不觉得呀
Doesn't seem that long to me.

566
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:31,970
下个礼拜我想再进一批货
I have another shipment nextweek.

567
00:46:32,330 --> 00:46:33,350
不过这次
But this time

568
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:37,060
我想找一些生面孔 又靠的住的兄弟
I'm using some tough, new faces.

569
00:46:37,290 --> 00:46:38,410
你们休息一下
So you guys can rest.

570
00:46:42,080 --> 00:46:43,440
傻强他们也不用啊?
Even Keung and the others?

571
00:46:44,160 --> 00:46:45,390
傻强?
Keung?

572
00:46:48,290 --> 00:46:50,450
傻强是傻瓜嘛
Don't you know he's nuts?

573
00:47:02,910 --> 00:47:04,540
你知道吧 公司里有内鬼
There's a mole within us. You know that?

574
00:47:11,580 --> 00:47:12,810
你觉得应该怎样做?
What do you think we should do?

575
00:47:14,500 --> 00:47:15,520
我解决它
I'll take care of it.

576
00:47:16,500 --> 00:47:17,620
怎么解决?
How?

577
00:47:29,660 --> 00:47:32,960
这两天我会把他揪出来 你准备一下
I'll find outwho he is in a couple of days. Get ready for action.

578
00:47:35,790 --> 00:47:36,950
阿仁
Yan.

579
00:47:39,870 --> 00:47:41,570
这么多兄弟 我最信你了
Of all the brothers, I trust you the most.

580
00:48:06,450 --> 00:48:09,080
小刘 小刘 早啊 来来来来
Lau.

581
00:48:16,370 --> 00:48:17,460
来一根 不要了
No, thanks

582
00:48:22,750 --> 00:48:23,970
兄弟们
These folks.

583
00:48:24,370 --> 00:48:26,570
差不多你都认识 用不着介绍了
You know most of them no need for introduction, right?

584
00:48:27,250 --> 00:48:28,900
不是 我是说...
No, but...

585
00:48:28,980 --> 00:48:29,970
怎么?
Why?

586
00:48:30,290 --> 00:48:31,190
他们怎么?
They are so...

587
00:48:33,410 --> 00:48:35,940
在这时候来啊 谁都知道你查内鬼
Who doesn't know you're sent here to find the mole?

588
00:48:36,160 --> 00:48:38,130
怎么样?来杯咖啡吧?
What do you want them to do? Pour you a cup of coffee?

589
00:48:38,910 --> 00:48:41,640
不遭人嫉是庸才 对不对?
Only an idiot will not be envied, right?

590
00:48:42,040 --> 00:48:44,560
不不过他们谁都想查出来那个内鬼到底是谁
They all want to know who the mole is

591
00:48:44,950 --> 00:48:46,650
如果你想查谁尽管说
Just tell me whom you want to investigate.

592
00:48:46,660 --> 00:48:47,590
好
OK.

593
00:48:48,540 --> 00:48:49,630
有线索吗?
Any clues?

594
00:48:52,160 --> 00:48:53,460
两天以前呢 我的卧底
Two days ago, my informer

595
00:48:53,660 --> 00:48:55,860
差一点查到这个内鬼是谁
nearly found outwho he was.

596
00:48:56,160 --> 00:48:57,290
不过可惜被他跑了
Too bad he lost him.

597
00:48:57,620 --> 00:48:58,950
但我想韩琛要出货呢
But if Sam is getting a new shipment

598
00:48:59,250 --> 00:49:00,910
他一定会再找这个内鬼的
he must contact the mole again.

599
00:49:01,200 --> 00:49:03,170
我想盯着韩琛 应该行
Justfollow Sam and we'll getwhatwe want.

600
00:49:04,580 --> 00:49:06,270
有道理 多教我两招
That's right. I've much to learn from you.

601
00:49:06,660 --> 00:49:07,720
你千万别这么说
Don't say that.

602
00:49:08,000 --> 00:49:10,460
上头一定觉得你有本事才派你来的
Our seniors sent you here because they think you can do it.

603
00:49:10,750 --> 00:49:12,680
你以为内务部的工作谁做都行啊?
Not everyone can handle IA tasks.

604
00:49:12,950 --> 00:49:13,750
这里太闷了
It's stuffy here.

605
00:49:14,160 --> 00:49:15,150
出去聊吧
Let's get out of here.

606
00:49:15,410 --> 00:49:17,470
重案组的咖啡啊 是总部最好的
The coffee here is the best in the headquarters.

607
00:49:17,660 --> 00:49:18,560
你也来一杯
I'll pour you a cup.

608
00:49:43,620 --> 00:49:47,520
我的卧底差一点查到这个内鬼是谁
My informer nearly found outwho the mole was.

609
00:49:47,910 --> 00:49:49,310
但我想韩琛要出货呢
But if Sam is getting a new shipment

610
00:49:49,620 --> 00:49:51,490
他一定会再找那个内鬼
he must contact the mole again.

611
00:50:56,700 --> 00:50:57,430
喂?
Yes?

612
00:50:57,700 --> 00:50:58,570
喂
Hey.

613
00:50:58,790 --> 00:50:59,880
怎么?
Yes?

614
00:51:00,160 --> 00:51:01,390
床到了
The bed has arrived.

615
00:51:01,750 --> 00:51:03,270
到啦?舒不舒服?
Is that so? Comfortable?

616
00:51:04,410 --> 00:51:05,470
你要不要试一试啊?
You want to try it?

617
00:51:05,700 --> 00:51:08,300
神经 赶稿子呢
Don't be silly. I have work to do.

618
00:51:09,580 --> 00:51:10,810
考虑一下
Think about it.

619
00:51:12,830 --> 00:51:14,690
不考虑 不考虑
No, I can't.

620
00:51:14,910 --> 00:51:15,740
来嘛
Come on.

621
00:51:15,910 --> 00:51:16,900
下个星期六
Saturday.

622
00:51:17,330 --> 00:51:18,520
下个星期六有空再跟你试
I'll be free next Saturday. We can try it then.

623
00:51:19,250 --> 00:51:20,300
好吧
OK.

624
00:51:20,660 --> 00:51:21,460
星期六
OK, next Saturday then.

625
00:51:21,700 --> 00:51:22,070
再见
Bye.

626
00:51:22,370 --> 00:51:23,100
Bye
Bye.

627
00:51:27,370 --> 00:51:28,060
醒了?
Up already?

628
00:51:28,250 --> 00:51:29,370
醒了
Yes.

629
00:51:31,000 --> 00:51:33,230
你刚刚试完床 又工作啦?
We just tested the bed and you are working again?

630
00:51:34,000 --> 00:51:35,760
勤奋嘛
I'm very hardworking.

631
00:51:36,830 --> 00:51:37,850
写到哪儿啦?
What are you writing now?

632
00:51:38,120 --> 00:51:39,380
写到这里了
Here.

633
00:51:41,040 --> 00:51:43,840
其实这本书的男主角挺惨的
The more I think of it, the more pathetic the main character appears.

634
00:51:44,410 --> 00:51:45,440
恩 很惨
Pathetic indeed.

635
00:51:46,410 --> 00:51:47,940
真的?那写好一点
Perhaps I should make him a happier guy.

636
00:51:48,290 --> 00:51:49,020
好 好
Good.

637
00:51:49,290 --> 00:51:50,950
写他做回好人吧
Should I turn him into a good guy?

638
00:51:53,660 --> 00:51:56,760
他是个好人 不过他又做错事
Even though he is good he has done bad things.

639
00:51:57,040 --> 00:51:58,160
那结局应该怎么样啊?
So how should it end?

640
00:51:58,660 --> 00:52:00,930
结局呢也是个问题
That's a good question.

641
00:52:01,250 --> 00:52:03,410
不过就留给你们这些文人吧
I'll leave this to you writers.

642
00:52:04,410 --> 00:52:06,110
你不睡?帮帮忙嘛
You're not going to sleep? Help me, please.

643
00:52:06,330 --> 00:52:08,260
你不睡?
Help me, please?

644
00:52:08,580 --> 00:52:09,510
我不行
I can't.

645
00:52:09,790 --> 00:52:11,720
你先睡吧 你太累了
Go to sleep. You are tired.

646
00:52:29,330 --> 00:52:31,090
大B 从今天开始
From now on

647
00:52:31,330 --> 00:52:32,420
二十四小时跟着黄警官
follow SP Wong around the clock.

648
00:52:36,000 --> 00:52:40,360
迪路啊 我知道怎么样分辨谁是警察了
Piero, I know how to spot a plainclothes.

649
00:52:41,160 --> 00:52:42,090
怎么分?
How?

650
00:52:42,410 --> 00:52:44,040
总之那个人在做事情
If he seems to be doing something

651
00:52:44,250 --> 00:52:46,540
但又不专心的做事情看着我们的
but is paying attention to us instead

652
00:52:47,040 --> 00:52:48,370
那就应该是警察
then he is a cop.

653
00:53:08,580 --> 00:53:10,310
对呀
Is that so?

654
00:53:11,200 --> 00:53:12,230
满街都是警察?
Then the whole place is filled with cops.

655
00:53:12,500 --> 00:53:13,690
好多的啊
They're everywhere.

656
00:53:23,540 --> 00:53:24,440
阿仁
Yan.

657
00:53:25,330 --> 00:53:26,160
琛哥
Boss.

658
00:53:40,910 --> 00:53:41,880
看什么?
Watching something?

659
00:53:42,330 --> 00:53:43,350
你是警察
You are a cop.

660
00:53:44,330 --> 00:53:46,490
我们在猜谁是警察
We are guessing who a cop is.

661
00:53:47,080 --> 00:53:48,840
靠 这么无聊
How trivial.

662
00:53:50,950 --> 00:53:51,890
按摩去不去?
I'm going for a massage, wanna come?

663
00:53:52,120 --> 00:53:53,110
我最讨厌了
I hate it.

664
00:53:53,910 --> 00:53:55,110
别跟人说哦
Don't tell.

665
00:53:56,950 --> 00:53:57,920
我就说
Tell on him.

666
00:53:58,160 --> 00:53:58,960
我不说
I won't.

667
00:54:06,410 --> 00:54:07,440
这么巧?
What a coincidence.

668
00:54:07,660 --> 00:54:09,930
对呀 刚好在这附近买东西
Yes, I was shopping in the hood.

669
00:54:11,000 --> 00:54:12,120
很久没见了
Haven't seen you for ages.

670
00:54:13,370 --> 00:54:14,740
六 七年了吧
6 or 7 years already

671
00:54:17,620 --> 00:54:18,610
还好吗?
How are you?

672
00:54:19,290 --> 00:54:21,620
我结婚了 你呢?
I'm married. How about you?

673
00:54:22,040 --> 00:54:24,340
还在道上混?
Still working in...?

674
00:54:30,540 --> 00:54:31,530
妈咪
Mommy.

675
00:54:34,790 --> 00:54:35,620
你女儿啊?
Your daughter?

676
00:54:35,790 --> 00:54:36,650
嗯
Yes.

677
00:54:39,330 --> 00:54:40,230
多大了?
How old is she?

678
00:54:40,500 --> 00:54:41,460
五岁
5 years old.

679
00:54:42,660 --> 00:54:46,460
我在等我老公来接我 所以...
I'm waiting for my husband's car, so...

680
00:54:46,910 --> 00:54:48,000
我也赶时间
I'm also in a hurry.

681
00:54:48,950 --> 00:54:49,680
Bye
Bye.

682
00:54:49,700 --> 00:54:50,760
Bye
Bye.

683
00:54:54,660 --> 00:54:57,260
妈咪 我今年六岁啦
Mommy, I'm 6 already.

684
00:54:57,660 --> 00:55:00,190
对不起 妈咪说错了
Sorry, I always get itwrong.

685
00:55:35,620 --> 00:55:36,550
你在哪啊?
Where are you now?

686
00:55:36,700 --> 00:55:37,600
正过来啦
On my way.

687
00:55:46,500 --> 00:55:47,220
喂
Hello?

688
00:55:48,000 --> 00:55:50,960
头 搭站坐地铁过海
Boss, he is taking the subway.

689
00:55:52,910 --> 00:55:53,810
跟着他
Keep following him.

690
00:56:16,580 --> 00:56:20,010
喂 头 他上了24楼
Boss, he has gone to the 24th floor.

691
00:56:20,330 --> 00:56:21,560
继续监视他
Stay put. Don't do anything rash.

692
00:56:38,160 --> 00:56:39,890
琛哥 查到了
Boss, we've got him.

693
00:56:42,120 --> 00:56:42,980
不知道
I don't know yet.

694
00:56:43,540 --> 00:56:44,940
不过我知道他现在在哪
But I know where he is now.

695
00:56:52,120 --> 00:56:53,210
在这里盯着
Keep watch over here.

696
00:57:10,660 --> 00:57:12,060
怎么样?有什么好消息?
So? Any good news?

697
00:57:12,330 --> 00:57:13,260
下个星期有批货到
A shipmentwill come in nextweek.

698
00:57:13,500 --> 00:57:14,760
时间地点还不知道
Time and location yet to be confirmed.

699
00:57:15,370 --> 00:57:17,100
韩琛的卧底到现在还没有查到
I still don't know who Sam's mole is

700
00:57:17,500 --> 00:57:19,460
不过他好像很有把握把我挖出来
but he seems confident he can blow my cover.

701
00:57:21,870 --> 00:57:23,390
把你挖出来?
In that case

702
00:57:29,290 --> 00:57:31,410
这样的话不要玩啦 我们输定了
we'd better stop it. We're gonna lose for sure.

703
00:57:32,120 --> 00:57:33,380
不会吧?
You are kidding, right?

704
00:57:33,660 --> 00:57:35,890
什么不会?会死人的
What else can we do? It's deadly business.

705
00:57:38,160 --> 00:57:39,150
喂
Hello?

706
00:57:41,540 --> 00:57:44,060
琛哥打电话来说 找到了那个内鬼
Boss said he had found the mole.

707
00:57:44,330 --> 00:57:45,260
叫我们去解决他
He told us to take care of him.

708
00:57:46,750 --> 00:57:47,730
我马上到
I'll be right there.

709
00:58:08,330 --> 00:58:09,260
喂
Hello?

710
00:58:10,620 --> 00:58:11,250
看着黄警官
Keep an eye on SP Wong.

711
00:58:26,870 --> 00:58:29,030
大个子 阿牛 走楼梯
You two, take the stairs.

712
00:58:29,950 --> 00:58:31,440
傻强 坐那部电梯
Keung. take the elevator.

713
00:58:32,660 --> 00:58:34,060
有没有人知道你来见我?
Anyone knows you're seeing me today?

714
00:58:34,250 --> 00:58:35,010
没有
No.

715
00:58:35,330 --> 00:58:36,350
现在他们在楼下
They are downstairs now.

716
00:59:04,790 --> 00:59:05,780
干什么?
What are you doing?

717
00:59:06,160 --> 00:59:07,320
把它收起来
Put it away.

718
00:59:33,330 --> 00:59:34,560
你从上面走吧
Take the window-washing scaffolding.

719
00:59:34,750 --> 00:59:35,640
你呢?
How about you?

720
00:59:36,200 --> 00:59:37,230
我坐电梯咯
I'll take the elevator.

721
00:59:39,450 --> 00:59:40,440
小心
Be careful.

722
00:59:44,700 --> 00:59:45,640
没什么
Nothing.

723
01:00:24,830 --> 01:00:27,760
喂 老婆 观澜湖的楼好棒啊
Darling, the apartment is superb.

724
01:00:28,000 --> 01:00:30,730
一百八十度玻璃 正对着高尔夫球场啊
A 180-degree window facing the golf course

725
01:00:31,040 --> 01:00:32,530
还有会籍啊 一百万都不用啊
plus club membership costs less than a million.

726
01:00:39,120 --> 01:00:40,110
黄警官
Superintendent Wong?

727
01:00:50,950 --> 01:00:52,280
麻烦你 兜去正门
Turn around to the main entrance.

728
01:01:45,620 --> 01:01:46,990
你觉得我这人怎么样?
What do you think of me?

729
01:01:53,870 --> 01:01:56,360
二十五号是你的生日嘛 臭小子
Your birthday is on the 25th, right?

730
01:02:16,950 --> 01:02:17,920
仁哥 快走啊
Let's go.

731
01:02:18,120 --> 01:02:19,210
警察!走啊!
Police. Let's go.

732
01:02:50,540 --> 01:02:51,900
头 麻烦了
Bad news, Boss.

733
01:02:52,160 --> 01:02:53,150
黄Sir出事了
Something happened to SP Wong.

734
01:03:45,250 --> 01:03:47,940
下午时分 在上环区发生的枪击案
There's a gunfight in Sheung Wan this afternoon.

735
01:03:48,160 --> 01:03:49,250
三名凶徒死亡
Three suspects were dead

736
01:03:49,500 --> 01:03:51,990
另外多名凶徒 警员和市民受伤
several suspects and pedestrians were injured.

737
01:03:52,250 --> 01:03:54,510
警方证实 其中一名死者的身份
The police confirmed that one of the victims

738
01:03:54,700 --> 01:03:56,470
是有组织及三合会调查科
was a superintendent in OCTB

739
01:03:56,660 --> 01:03:57,720
警司黄志诚
Mr Wong Chi-shing.

740
01:03:58,000 --> 01:03:59,120
行凶动机未明
The motive is unknown.

741
01:03:59,370 --> 01:04:01,130
警方不排除有仇杀成份
Possibility of gang feud is not ruled out.

742
01:04:01,450 --> 01:04:02,850
现正通缉多名活跃于
They are now after several triad members

743
01:04:03,120 --> 01:04:04,880
油尖旺区的黑社会分子
active in the Southern Kowloon area.

744
01:04:05,120 --> 01:04:06,590
警务处长发表声明
The Police Commissioner

745
01:04:06,830 --> 01:04:09,460
对黄志诚警司的死表示沉重的哀悼
expressed deep condolence

746
01:04:09,660 --> 01:04:11,430
并且表示会尽快破案
and pledged to solve the case as soon as possible.

747
01:04:12,700 --> 01:04:14,230
嘿 你都不知道刚才多险哪
Itwas a close shave.

748
01:04:14,790 --> 01:04:16,450
你一说去按摩啊 都不到十分钟
10 minutes after you went to your massage

749
01:04:16,660 --> 01:04:18,390
琛哥就说要做事了
Boss told us to get ready.

750
01:04:19,700 --> 01:04:21,230
哇 我真是怕
I was scared stiff.

751
01:04:21,750 --> 01:04:24,770
你知道我 一向来真格的溜到最后的嘛
You know, I hide under the car in every fight.

752
01:04:26,830 --> 01:04:28,590
上去还有枪嘛
And there were guns up there.

753
01:04:29,290 --> 01:04:32,520
我真想跟大家说 哇 我有事先走啦
I wanted to just sneak out of there.

754
01:04:36,500 --> 01:04:40,800
前两天 琛哥他叫我去他的房间里头
Two days ago, Boss told me to go to his room.

755
01:04:41,200 --> 01:04:43,470
他问我:傻强啊 你跟我多久了?
He asked me how long I'd worked for him.

756
01:04:43,790 --> 01:04:45,020
我哪记得
How the hell could I remember?

757
01:04:46,660 --> 01:04:48,190
然后他就说:傻强
He then said: Keung

758
01:04:49,330 --> 01:04:50,920
你跟我五年了
it's been 5 years already.

759
01:04:52,750 --> 01:04:55,270
你在这几年里头呢 都很能干
You've performed well all these years.

760
01:04:56,330 --> 01:04:58,160
如果我有个问题想问你
I have a question for you.

761
01:04:59,450 --> 01:05:02,150
就是说如果有兄弟是卧底
If one of your brothers is a mole

762
01:05:02,500 --> 01:05:03,760
你敢不敢杀了他?
will you dare to take him out?

763
01:05:04,620 --> 01:05:07,050
他就这样面对面问我 我当然说敢啦
Of course I said yes to his face.

764
01:05:07,330 --> 01:05:08,920
你当我真的是傻瓜啊?
You think I'm an idiot?

765
01:05:12,660 --> 01:05:14,060
结果怎么样呢
What's the result?

766
01:05:14,500 --> 01:05:16,830
当然是找不到那个卧底啦
Of course they couldn'tfind the mole.

767
01:05:18,870 --> 01:05:20,570
哇 那个警察硬骨头
The cop was tough.

768
01:05:21,330 --> 01:05:22,490
把他抓了上去
They dragged him upstairs

769
01:05:22,830 --> 01:05:25,320
他们把他抓了上去 足足打了十分钟
and beat him up for a good 10 minutes.

770
01:05:26,450 --> 01:05:27,780
十分钟
10 minutes...

771
01:05:31,910 --> 01:05:33,240
十分钟
10 minutes...

772
01:05:34,950 --> 01:05:36,580
一句话都没有说过
He didn't say a word.

773
01:05:43,200 --> 01:05:44,100
傻强
Keung.

774
01:05:46,700 --> 01:05:47,860
琛哥说
Boss said...

775
01:05:49,290 --> 01:05:51,220
那个警察很会掩饰
the cop was hot on his trail.

776
01:05:54,870 --> 01:05:57,900
今天谁没出现 谁就是卧底
Who didn't show up today is the mole.

777
01:05:58,950 --> 01:06:00,110
我没有
I didn't...

778
01:06:00,700 --> 01:06:02,430
我没说你去按摩
tell him you wentfor a massage.

779
01:06:04,040 --> 01:06:07,370
让琛哥知道你去按摩 你肯定倒霉了
If Boss knew, you're dead meat.

780
01:06:10,200 --> 01:06:13,370
仁哥 我好想问你
Yan, I want to ask you something.

781
01:06:13,660 --> 01:06:15,820
今天那个按摩女郎漂亮吗?
How was the masseuse today?

782
01:06:18,000 --> 01:06:19,260
你知道
Because...

783
01:06:20,660 --> 01:06:23,220
按摩女郎不漂亮那就没劲了
if she's ugly, it's notworth it.

784
01:06:29,080 --> 01:06:30,340
快走
Leave right away.

785
01:06:31,330 --> 01:06:33,800
撞了车 很多警察会来
There will be lots of cops after a car crash.

786
01:06:37,500 --> 01:06:40,120
总之呢 你要记住
Anyway, remember this:

787
01:06:42,290 --> 01:06:44,310
如果哪个人
If you see someone

788
01:06:45,580 --> 01:06:50,780
他做事不专心 又看着你的话
doing something without paying attention to it but at the same time watching you

789
01:06:53,950 --> 01:06:55,750
他就是警察
then he is a cop.

790
01:07:41,000 --> 01:07:42,390
根据闭路电视的录像
According to the closed-circuit TV

791
01:07:42,660 --> 01:07:44,860
黄警司是四点十五分进入大厦
SP Wong entered that building at 4:15 pm.

792
01:07:45,120 --> 01:07:47,780
凶徒二十分钟后到达
The suspects entered 20 minutes later.

793
01:07:49,160 --> 01:07:50,960
在四点三十八分
At 4:38 pm

794
01:07:51,290 --> 01:07:53,080
我们收到刘警官的通知
we received Inspector Lau's report.

795
01:07:54,750 --> 01:07:58,440
在我们到达大厦前八分钟 有人堕楼
8 minutes before we arrived, someone fell off the building.

796
01:07:59,910 --> 01:08:01,170
那个是黄警司
That was SP Wong.

797
01:08:02,120 --> 01:08:05,580
死的和受伤的疑凶 全都是韩琛的手下
All the suspects killed or injured belong to Sam's gang.

798
01:08:06,410 --> 01:08:07,940
有很多疑凶跑了
Many suspects escaped.

799
01:08:08,790 --> 01:08:09,980
人数不清楚
The actual numbers are unknown.

800
01:08:10,660 --> 01:08:12,650
知不知道黄警司去那儿干什么
Do you know why SP Wong went to that building?

801
01:08:17,160 --> 01:08:18,360
是我
Itwas me.

802
01:08:18,830 --> 01:08:20,300
我叫CIB跟踪他
I told CIB to follow him.

803
01:08:20,580 --> 01:08:22,310
你们CIB为什么跟踪黄警司?
Why was CIB following him?

804
01:08:22,830 --> 01:08:24,260
这是内务部的事
That's IA's business.

805
01:08:25,160 --> 01:08:26,530
现在黄警司死了
Now that SP Wong is dead

806
01:08:26,830 --> 01:08:28,130
就和我们重案组有关系
it is OCTB's business.

807
01:08:28,450 --> 01:08:29,680
你这是什么态度啊?
What kind of attitude is that?

808
01:08:29,910 --> 01:08:32,140
黄警司尽忠职守 你找人调查他?
SP Wong was dedicated to the police force and you investigated him?

809
01:08:32,410 --> 01:08:34,070
内务部又是什么态度啊?
What kind of attitude is that?

810
01:08:34,330 --> 01:08:35,660
我们高层的事用不着你管?
So we seniors have to ask for your approval, huh?

811
01:08:35,910 --> 01:08:37,000
现在你的人做错了
Your people have made a mistake now.

812
01:08:37,290 --> 01:08:38,750
不然黄警司不会死 知道吗?
Or SP Wong wouldn't have died.

813
01:08:39,000 --> 01:08:39,960
现在我跟你谈公事
I am talking about business here.

814
01:08:40,250 --> 01:08:41,300
我跟你谈私事
I am talking about personal matters.

815
01:08:41,500 --> 01:08:43,260
谁也想不到会这样 OK?
Nobody wanted this, OK?

816
01:08:49,410 --> 01:08:50,400
对不起
Sorry, sir.

817
01:08:52,950 --> 01:08:54,250
是我的疏忽
It's my negligence.

818
01:08:56,790 --> 01:08:58,550
我会给大家一个交代
I will give everybody an answer.

819
01:08:59,330 --> 01:09:00,190
对不起
Sorry.

820
01:09:05,120 --> 01:09:06,710
黄警司的计算机里面
SP Wong has a file

821
01:09:07,000 --> 01:09:08,960
有他派去韩琛那里做卧底的档案
with information on our undercover in Sam's gang.

822
01:09:09,580 --> 01:09:11,340
不过有密码锁着
It is locked by a password.

823
01:09:11,790 --> 01:09:13,620
但是计算机部的同事又解不开
The technical staff can't decipher it.

824
01:09:14,580 --> 01:09:15,070
刘警官
Inspector Lau.

825
01:09:15,290 --> 01:09:15,950
嗯
Yes.

826
01:09:16,200 --> 01:09:18,300
你跟CIB 尽快想办法
Work with CIB

827
01:09:18,540 --> 01:09:19,470
把它打开
to unlock it.

828
01:09:19,790 --> 01:09:21,690
把那个卧底找出来 OK?
Find our man and get him out of there.

829
01:09:23,750 --> 01:09:24,770
还有
By the way

830
01:09:26,330 --> 01:09:27,850
黄警司是个好警察
SP Wong was a good cop.

831
01:09:28,950 --> 01:09:32,450
他的葬礼 你们要办得风光一点
We should give him a grand funeral.

832
01:09:33,120 --> 01:09:33,810
知道吗?
Okay?

833
01:09:34,450 --> 01:09:35,480
是 长官
Yes, sir.

834
01:09:47,290 --> 01:09:48,080
喂?
Hello?

835
01:09:48,700 --> 01:09:52,100
喂 琛哥啊 怎么闹的这么大?
Boss. Why made such a scene?

836
01:09:52,950 --> 01:09:54,110
那警察整天跟着我
He was following me all the time.

837
01:09:54,330 --> 01:09:55,730
不是他死就是我亡啊
One of us would have to die.

838
01:09:56,000 --> 01:09:57,390
这现在全由我负责
I'm now in charge of everything here.

839
01:09:57,660 --> 01:09:59,190
如果要出货 打个电话给我
If you're having any transactions just let me know.

840
01:09:59,450 --> 01:10:00,440
搞定了
It's done.

841
01:10:00,790 --> 01:10:03,480
今天杀那警察的时候 那批货已经收了
We got the goods when they killed the cop today.

842
01:10:04,160 --> 01:10:07,890
哪 不多说了哦 免得你烦
Okay, I won't bother you now.

843
01:12:15,040 --> 01:12:16,230
为什么找我?
What did you call me for?

844
01:12:19,040 --> 01:12:20,300
你就是那张牌?
So you're the one?

845
01:12:22,700 --> 01:12:23,670
你是谁?
Who are you?

846
01:12:23,910 --> 01:12:25,400
重案组刘健明
Inspector Lau of OCTB.

847
01:12:31,250 --> 01:12:33,510
黄警司死了 大家都很不开心
SP Wong is gone. We're all upset

848
01:12:34,410 --> 01:12:35,900
我还有点事情没做完
I still have unfinished business.

849
01:12:37,000 --> 01:12:40,230
我看黄警司不想知道你犯法
SP Wong wouldn'twant you to take law in your hands.

850
01:12:40,580 --> 01:12:41,740
你到底想怎么样?
What do you want?

851
01:12:43,410 --> 01:12:44,400
合作
Co-operation.

852
01:12:45,450 --> 01:12:49,180
我想我们两个合作可以反转韩琛
We can nail Sam by joining force.

853
01:12:54,080 --> 01:12:56,770
今天下午 在上环发生的枪击案
The police has discovered

854
01:12:57,000 --> 01:12:58,660
其中一名在逃的疑犯
the body of a fugitive suspect. He was involved in

855
01:12:58,950 --> 01:13:01,950
警方在一小时前发现他的尸体
the Sheung Wan shooting earlier today.

856
01:13:02,160 --> 01:13:03,150
经警方证实
The police has confirmed

857
01:13:03,410 --> 01:13:06,580
是派去执行职务的卧底警察徐伟强
the body to be an undercover cop Tsui Wai-keung

858
01:13:06,830 --> 01:13:08,760
警方对事件深表惋惜
The police has expressed their condolence

859
01:13:09,080 --> 01:13:09,940
并表示会尽力追查
and promised a thorough investigation.

860
01:13:10,160 --> 01:13:11,320
老板 仁哥回来了
Boss, Yan is back.

861
01:13:12,000 --> 01:13:14,830
今天下午 元朗发生连环三车相撞
Three vehicles collided in Yuen Long today.

862
01:13:15,120 --> 01:13:16,550
其中一辆轿车的司机被困
The driver of the private car was trapped

863
01:13:16,830 --> 01:13:18,390
由消防员救出
until firefighters came and rescued him.

864
01:13:21,540 --> 01:13:22,440
琛哥
Boss.

865
01:13:23,500 --> 01:13:24,390
怎么样?阿仁
What is it, Yan?

866
01:13:25,750 --> 01:13:27,210
我干掉了傻强
I have taken care of Keung already.

867
01:13:29,120 --> 01:13:30,640
有没有找人看过那货仓?
Did you ever send him to the warehouse?

868
01:13:32,200 --> 01:13:33,860
如果他知道在哪就麻烦了
Itwill be disastrous if he knows where it is.

869
01:13:44,250 --> 01:13:45,370
琛哥
Boss. It's me.

870
01:13:45,700 --> 01:13:46,730
你用不着自己去吧
You don't have to go yourself.

871
01:13:47,000 --> 01:13:48,050
我不想有人知道密码
I don'twant anyone to know the password.

872
01:13:48,450 --> 01:13:49,390
明白
I understand.

873
01:13:49,870 --> 01:13:51,030
我帮你把人调开
I'll send everyone away.

874
01:14:00,080 --> 01:14:00,910
张警官
Inspector Cheung.

875
01:14:03,250 --> 01:14:04,870
叫跟踪韩琛的人回来
Tell those boys to stop following Sam's gang.

876
01:14:09,870 --> 01:14:12,500
我收到消息 韩琛正要去他的货仓
I got information that Sam is heading towards the warehouse.

877
01:14:12,660 --> 01:14:14,930
不撤走跟踪他的人 他是不会去货仓的
He won't go if he's being tailed.

878
01:14:17,410 --> 01:14:18,340
要是真想帮黄警司
Just call them back.

879
01:14:18,660 --> 01:14:20,100
做点事的话就现在下班
Let's do something for SP Wong.

880
01:14:20,330 --> 01:14:21,660
你们帮帮忙好不好?
Please help me, OK?

881
01:14:22,500 --> 01:14:24,430
你说句话嘛
Say something.

882
01:14:25,330 --> 01:14:27,060
这件事跟我无关
This is not my case.

883
01:14:27,620 --> 01:14:29,650
陈警司叫我别碰这件事
Officer Chan told me not to get involved.

884
01:14:30,830 --> 01:14:34,260
如果大家肯下班 那下班咯
If they're willing to get off duty then it's up to them.

885
01:14:34,830 --> 01:14:37,590
我知道黄警司的事情我要负上责任
I know I'm responsible for SP Wong's death.

886
01:14:37,870 --> 01:14:38,670
但我跟大家一样
I am also a cop, like you.

887
01:14:38,950 --> 01:14:40,980
我也是警察 我也是为了破案
I want to solve the case too.

888
01:14:41,660 --> 01:14:43,220
你不是只想升职的吗?
I thought you only want promotion.

889
01:14:45,910 --> 01:14:47,640
哪 是黄警司的卧底给的情报
It's SP Wong's mole who tipped me off.

890
01:14:47,870 --> 01:14:48,630
你们信不信?
Do you believe it or not?

891
01:14:48,910 --> 01:14:50,880
过了今晚可能就没机会了 你们想清楚啊
This is our last chance Are you ready to take the risk?

892
01:15:39,700 --> 01:15:41,530
各单位注意 目标车辆
Attention: Target vehicle

893
01:15:41,830 --> 01:15:43,760
现在由广东道转至三号干线
is on Highway no.3 from Canton Road.

894
01:15:51,500 --> 01:15:52,660
三号码头调头
It's turning around at Pier 3

895
01:15:52,950 --> 01:15:54,320
上龙翔道往观塘方向
on Lung Cheung Road towards Kwun Tong.

896
01:16:07,450 --> 01:16:08,440
张警官 他们来了二十分钟
They have been here for 20 minutes

897
01:16:08,700 --> 01:16:10,330
上了大厦停车场四楼
they are going to the 4th floor of the car park.

898
01:16:30,200 --> 01:16:33,100
干什么?这案子陈警司不让我碰
Officer Chan won't let me touch this case.

899
01:16:33,450 --> 01:16:35,680
出了娄子 你可自己负责
If anything goes wrong, you'll take the blame.

900
01:16:41,290 --> 01:16:42,850
他们正在4P点货
They are loading the goods at 4P.

901
01:16:43,080 --> 01:16:45,010
大象 在3P的出口准备
Elephant, stand by at the exit at 3P.

902
01:16:45,200 --> 01:16:46,930
小八 守住2P的入口位置
Double Eight, watch the entrance at 2P.

903
01:16:47,160 --> 01:16:49,390
还有 鱼丸和张警官会在这里准备
Fishball and Cheung, stand by here.

904
01:16:49,660 --> 01:16:51,190
所有人等我的命令
All of you, waitfor my signal.

905
01:17:10,290 --> 01:17:12,150
唉 忘了琛哥叫我垫后了
Oh, I forgot Boss told me to stay behind.

906
01:17:12,410 --> 01:17:13,400
在前面放下我
Drop me off here.

907
01:17:59,580 --> 01:18:00,240
撞他!
Run him over.

908
01:18:51,830 --> 01:18:53,060
我算过命
My Master always said that about my life:

909
01:18:54,040 --> 01:18:57,530
算命的说我是:一将功成万骨枯
"What thousands must die so that Caesar may become great."

910
01:18:58,660 --> 01:19:01,830
路怎样走 你们自己挑了
You choose your own future.

911
01:19:16,410 --> 01:19:17,400
你挑的
That's what you have chosen.

912
01:19:54,950 --> 01:19:56,920
这杯咖啡是给你的
Coffee for you.

913
01:20:04,620 --> 01:20:05,610
他等了你很久了
He's waited a long time for you.

914
01:20:15,660 --> 01:20:16,860
是你呀?
So it's you?

915
01:20:22,330 --> 01:20:23,320
那台机器怎么样?
Was the stereo OK?

916
01:20:23,580 --> 01:20:24,600
很好
Pretty good.

917
01:20:25,500 --> 01:20:26,830
胆机要预热
Those tube amps have to be warmed up.

918
01:20:27,120 --> 01:20:29,250
预热十数分钟 声音更漂亮
Wait 10 minutes and it sounds great.

919
01:20:30,120 --> 01:20:31,140
要不要给你送礼啊?
Should I salute you?

920
01:20:31,330 --> 01:20:32,350
不用
Not, don't.

921
01:20:34,290 --> 01:20:35,480
喂 做卧底多久了?
How long have you been an undercover?

922
01:20:36,290 --> 01:20:37,950
我跟了韩琛三年多
I've followed Sam for 3 years.

923
01:20:38,330 --> 01:20:39,800
以前跟过几个老大
I had several other bosses before.

924
01:20:40,370 --> 01:20:41,770
加起来差不多有十年吧
All together it's been 10 years.

925
01:20:42,040 --> 01:20:43,130
十年?
10 years?

926
01:20:43,450 --> 01:20:44,780
那应该我送礼给你才行啊
I should salute you instead.

927
01:20:45,000 --> 01:20:46,330
恢复我身份就行了
I just want an identity.

928
01:20:46,660 --> 01:20:47,960
我只想做个普通人
An identity as a normal man.

929
01:20:49,330 --> 01:20:50,230
厌了?
Getting tired?

930
01:20:52,080 --> 01:20:54,880
你没做过卧底 你不懂
You've never been a mole, you won't understand.

931
01:20:58,370 --> 01:21:00,000
可惜找不到那个内鬼
Too bad I still can'tfind the stooge.

932
01:21:00,330 --> 01:21:01,660
找到了我一定不放过他
I'll take him down if I find him.

933
01:21:08,330 --> 01:21:11,590
别想那么多了 给你恢复身份
Don'tworry. Let me give you back your identity.

934
01:21:12,000 --> 01:21:13,620
我帮你打开那个档案 可是
I'll open your file but...

935
01:21:14,000 --> 01:21:15,050
我没有密码
I don't have the password.

936
01:21:17,160 --> 01:21:18,720
卧底摩斯密码是什么?
What's the Morse code for "undercover"?

937
01:21:20,790 --> 01:21:22,050
就这么简单?
That's it?

938
01:22:08,660 --> 01:22:09,320
哇 你这么大个人
Are you serious?

939
01:22:09,580 --> 01:22:11,070
保镖的镖字都写错?
You don't even know to spell "bodyguard"?

940
01:22:11,580 --> 01:22:12,010
不是这个?
Isn't it supposed to look like this?

941
01:22:12,290 --> 01:22:13,550
当然不是这个啦
Of course not.

942
01:24:26,700 --> 01:24:27,640
李医生
Dr. Lee.

943
01:24:29,040 --> 01:24:30,200
还以为你不会来呢
I thought you wouldn't come.

944
01:24:30,540 --> 01:24:31,970
警方在通缉你
You're wanted by the police.

945
01:24:33,870 --> 01:24:35,340
能不能借你椅子睡一下?
Can I sleep in your chair again?

946
01:24:36,120 --> 01:24:37,490
上去慢慢说吧
Let's talk upstairs.

947
01:24:41,450 --> 01:24:43,180
你上次说你是警察
Last time you said you're a cop

948
01:24:44,000 --> 01:24:45,090
是真的?
Is it true?

949
01:24:45,790 --> 01:24:46,780
本来是
It was true.

950
01:24:47,830 --> 01:24:49,060
不知道现在还是不是
But I'm not so sure now.

951
01:24:54,410 --> 01:24:55,970
那你有什么打算?
So what's your plan?

952
01:24:56,790 --> 01:24:59,480
不知道 正在想
I don't know. Still thinking.

953
01:25:13,750 --> 01:25:15,680
有件事我早就想跟你说了
There's one thing I've been trying to tell you for a while.

954
01:25:17,160 --> 01:25:18,790
不过一直觉得不好意思
But it's too embarrassing.

955
01:25:25,450 --> 01:25:27,390
我整天做梦见到你这件事
I told you I dreamt about you all the time.

956
01:25:28,290 --> 01:25:29,380
是真的
It's true.

957
01:25:37,750 --> 01:25:38,940
我也是
Me too.

958
01:26:22,910 --> 01:26:26,470
记着我们的秘密 再见
Remember my secret. Goodbye.

959
01:26:43,200 --> 01:26:44,170
Mary
Mary

960
01:26:45,250 --> 01:26:47,740
怎么了 坏了?
What is it? Has it broken down?

961
01:26:58,790 --> 01:27:00,910
今天早上音响铺的人来过
This morning the guys from the stereo shop came.

962
01:27:02,000 --> 01:27:03,830
他们帮你调过机器
They have tuned it up already.

963
01:27:05,660 --> 01:27:07,930
还留了张CD给你试机
They also left a CD samplerfor you.

964
01:27:09,160 --> 01:27:10,490
我听了
I've listened to it.

965
01:27:16,870 --> 01:27:18,460
你吃早餐没有?
Have you had breakfast yet?

966
01:27:18,910 --> 01:27:20,040
我去帮你买
I'll get you some.

967
01:27:21,370 --> 01:27:22,530
冻奶茶?
Iced tea?

968
01:27:23,660 --> 01:27:24,860
菠萝包?
Chinese buns?

969
01:27:26,120 --> 01:27:27,180
好
Sure.

970
01:27:43,000 --> 01:27:45,760
这本小说我写不下去了
I can'tfinish my novel.

971
01:27:49,790 --> 01:27:51,950
我都不知道那个人是好人坏人
I don't know whether he's good or bad.

972
01:27:55,290 --> 01:27:57,720
这个我看只有他自己清楚
I think only he knows.

973
01:27:59,580 --> 01:28:00,940
下个礼拜进货
A shipmentwill come in nextweek.

974
01:28:02,330 --> 01:28:03,590
风声紧
They are watching closely.

975
01:28:04,540 --> 01:28:06,060
你做你的事
You do what you need to do.

976
01:28:06,910 --> 01:28:08,500
我这边你不用担心
I will handle the rest.

977
01:28:10,120 --> 01:28:12,850
正在查内鬼 我怕我帮不了你
The file is open. I can't handle it.

978
01:28:13,160 --> 01:28:14,750
原来你不是担心我
So you're notworried about me.

979
01:28:16,290 --> 01:28:18,190
是担心你自己啊 刘警官
You are worried about yourself, Inspector Lau.

980
01:28:22,870 --> 01:28:24,100
声音漂亮吗?
Are the voices crisp enough?

981
01:28:24,410 --> 01:28:25,470
这些珍贵的录音
The precious recording

982
01:28:26,330 --> 01:28:28,320
是我在韩琛的办公室找到的
was taken from Sam's office.

983
01:28:29,330 --> 01:28:30,420
你不走运
It's not your lucky day.

984
01:28:31,370 --> 01:28:33,630
用不着唬我 想怎么样?
Don't threaten me. What do you want?

985
01:28:34,120 --> 01:28:35,380
我想恢复身份
I want my identity back.

986
01:28:36,330 --> 01:28:38,920
三点钟 港外线码头 开着电话
3 pm, Central Ferry Pier. Keep your cell on.

987
01:29:02,700 --> 01:29:05,230
你现在拨的电话暂时未能接通
The number you have dialed cannot be connected.

988
01:29:05,500 --> 01:29:07,550
请在讯号声后留下您的口讯
Please leave a message after the beep.

989
01:29:08,790 --> 01:29:10,720
Mary 对不起
Mary, I'm sorry.

990
01:29:11,910 --> 01:29:13,440
我选了做好人
I've chosen to be the good guy.

991
01:29:14,160 --> 01:29:15,820
我现在就去见陈永仁
I'm going to meet Yan now.

992
01:29:16,410 --> 01:29:19,250
不管怎么样 我会恢复他的身份
No matterwhat, I'll give him back his identity.

993
01:29:19,700 --> 01:29:21,430
档案就在我的计算机里面
The file is in my computer

994
01:29:22,040 --> 01:29:23,700
密码是你的生日
and the password is your birthday.

995
01:30:40,660 --> 01:30:41,890
挺利索的
You sure know what you're doing.

996
01:30:42,200 --> 01:30:43,670
我也读过警校
I also went to the cadet school.

997
01:30:47,330 --> 01:30:50,350
你们卧底可真有意思 老在天台见面
Do all undercover cops like rooftops?

998
01:30:52,370 --> 01:30:55,270
我不像你 我光明正大
Unlike you, I'm not afraid of light.

999
01:30:57,160 --> 01:30:58,420
我要的东西呢?
So where's the stuff I want?

1000
01:30:59,950 --> 01:31:02,220
我要的你还未必带来呢
I don't think you've broughtwhat I want either.

1001
01:31:07,330 --> 01:31:08,420
什么意思?
So what does that mean?

1002
01:31:09,500 --> 01:31:11,120
你上来晒太阳的?
We came up here to sunbathe?

1003
01:31:13,160 --> 01:31:14,630
给我一个机会
Give me a chance.

1004
01:31:16,000 --> 01:31:17,360
怎么给你机会?
How?

1005
01:31:19,450 --> 01:31:20,850
我以前没得选择
I have no choice before

1006
01:31:22,080 --> 01:31:24,050
现在我想做一个好人
but now I want to turn over a new leaf.

1007
01:31:28,200 --> 01:31:29,230
好啊
Good.

1008
01:31:31,500 --> 01:31:32,620
跟法官说
Try telling that to the judge.

1009
01:31:34,120 --> 01:31:35,610
看他让不让你做好人
See what he has to say.

1010
01:31:39,000 --> 01:31:40,490
那就是要我死?
You want me dead?

1011
01:31:40,870 --> 01:31:43,570
对不起 我是警察
Sorry, I'm a cop.

1012
01:31:43,750 --> 01:31:44,710
谁知道?
Who knows that?

1013
01:32:01,660 --> 01:32:02,790
别动 警察
Don't move. Police.

1014
01:32:04,000 --> 01:32:05,960
放下枪 放了刘警官
Drop your weapon and let Inspector Lau go first.

1015
01:32:06,450 --> 01:32:08,080
你上司是韩琛的卧底
Your boss is Sam's mole.

1016
01:32:08,330 --> 01:32:09,520
证据在我手上
I got evidence.

1017
01:32:09,830 --> 01:32:11,320
我们到警察局再说
Let's clear this up at the station.

1018
01:32:11,790 --> 01:32:13,810
放下枪 立刻放下枪
Drop your weapon now.

1019
01:32:14,080 --> 01:32:15,170
我报了警啦
I've called the police.

1020
01:32:15,410 --> 01:32:16,380
我干嘛要相信你啊?
Why should I trust you?

1021
01:32:16,660 --> 01:32:17,860
你不用相信我
You don't have to.

1022
01:32:41,540 --> 01:32:42,770
你小心点
You'd better watch out.

1023
01:32:44,290 --> 01:32:45,620
你小心点
Look who's talking.

1024
01:33:30,500 --> 01:33:33,950
祝你们在警察部一帆风顺
I wish you every success in the police force.

1025
01:33:36,370 --> 01:33:37,700
干杯 各位长官
Bottoms up, officers.

1026
01:33:40,830 --> 01:33:43,630
不用怕 大家同门师兄弟
No sweat. We are brothers.

1027
01:33:44,870 --> 01:33:46,270
现在琛哥死了
Sam is dead now.

1028
01:33:48,870 --> 01:33:50,060
以后你要罩着我
You have to look after me.

1029
01:33:57,200 --> 01:33:58,570
我九四年加入警校
I joined the cadet school in 1994.

1030
01:33:59,120 --> 01:34:02,110
可惜 这么多年都上不去
But my career never really takes off.

1031
01:34:03,500 --> 01:34:05,190
他连看都不看我一眼
Sam looked down on me.

1032
01:34:06,000 --> 01:34:07,760
韩琛的录音带我已经毁灭了
I've taken care of Sam's tape.

1033
01:34:08,370 --> 01:34:10,670
放心吧 以后我跟你了
Don'tworry. I'll follow you from now on.

1034
01:34:12,790 --> 01:34:15,880
警察快到了 做戏做全套
Ourfolks will be here any minute. Let's give them a good show.

1035
01:34:21,870 --> 01:34:25,330
其实我很能干 是琛哥不识货
I'm actually quite smart. Too bad Sam never knew that.

1036
01:35:06,160 --> 01:35:07,490
我是警察
I'm a cop.

1037
01:35:32,700 --> 01:35:35,070
六个月后 李心儿医生在去世的警校校长
Six months later, Dr. Lee Sum Yee was looking through the personal

1038
01:35:35,330 --> 01:35:36,960
叶Sir的遗物中 发现陈永仁的档案
properties left by Officer Yip Headmaster of the Cadet.

1039
01:35:37,000 --> 01:35:39,460
证实了他的警员的身份 陈永仁现
She found Chan Wing-yan's file that proved his police identity.

1040
01:35:39,540 --> 01:35:41,470
安葬在黄志诚警司的墓旁
Chan Wing-yan is now buried next to SP Wong Chi-shing.

1041
01:36:27,080 --> 01:36:29,050
你好吗?警察
How are you, Mr. Policeman?

1042
01:37:08,500 --> 01:37:11,400
不守规矩的人 就好像他这样
Those who break the rules will be like him

1043
01:37:11,790 --> 01:37:12,980
滚蛋
They will be expelled

1044
01:37:14,040 --> 01:37:16,010
你们有没有人想跟他交换?
Anybody wants to trade place with him?

1045
01:37:23,370 --> 01:37:24,770
我想跟他换
I do

1046
01:37:33,660 --> 01:37:34,630
佛曰:
Says the Buddha:

1047
01:37:34,660 --> 01:37:36,930
「受身无间者永远不死
"He who is in Continuous Hell never dies

1048
01:37:37,000 --> 01:37:39,960
寿长乃无间地狱中之大劫,」
Longevity is a big hardship in Continuous Hell"


